access

Class AbstractAccess<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • access.AbstractAccess<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - : the object for which this class is reflected
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientAccess, OrderAccess, OrderItemAccess, ProductAccess

    public class AbstractAccess<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the backbone for all the *Access.java classes. It provides methods and queries in order to perform the CRUD operations on all the tables in the "ordermng.db" database.
    Since:
    Apr 06, 2020
    Author:
    Coroian Tudor
